WEBVTT

00:00:06.365 --> 00:00:08.569
Tokom našeg životnog veka,

00:00:08.569 --> 00:00:12.809
naša tela prolaze kroz niz
neverovatnih promena:

00:00:12.809 --> 00:00:13.513
rastemo,

00:00:13.513 --> 00:00:14.661
prolazimo kroz pubertet,

00:00:14.661 --> 00:00:16.485
i mnogi se razmnožavaju.

00:00:16.485 --> 00:00:17.778
Iza scene,

00:00:17.778 --> 00:00:22.231
endokrini sistem neprestano
diriguje ovim promenama.

00:00:22.231 --> 00:00:24.853
Pored rasta i seksualne zrelosti,

00:00:24.853 --> 00:00:27.838
ovaj sistem reguliše sve, od spavanja

00:00:27.838 --> 00:00:30.220
do ritma otkucaja srca,